      <title>Hexo+GitHub Pages博客搭建</title>
      <link href="/2018/12/11/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>/2018/12/11/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p><h2 id="部署原理"><a href="#部署原理" class="headerlink" title="部署原理"></a>部署原理</h2><p><img src="/images/hexo%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9B%BE-3.png" alt="hexo部署图"><br>使用Hexo需要Node.js环境，假设环境准备完毕，通过命令<code>hexo g</code>(g代表generate)，Hexo会在本地生成源文件，然后通过<code>hexo d</code>(d代表deploy)，发布至远程GitHub，实线箭头部分即可满足使用和配置博客的需要，如果希望进行代码级改造，可使用GitHub Desktop操作.</p><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:center">名称</th><th style="text-align:center">版本</th><th style="text-align:center">说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center">电脑系统</td><td style="text-align:center">mac OS X EI Capitan 10.11.6</td><td style="text-align:center">使用终端操作命令，最好具备linux基础知识</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center">Node.js</td><td style="text-align:center">10.14.1</td><td style="text-align:center">Hexo能够运行的基础环境</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center">Hexo</td><td style="text-align:center">3.8.0</td><td style="text-align:center">生成静态页面到本地和发布到远程仓库的工具</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center">GitHub Web</td><td style="text-align:center"></td><td style="text-align:center">远程仓库，存储Hexo发布后的页面</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:center">GitHub Desktop</td><td style="text-align:center">1.5.0</td><td style="text-align:center">本地仓库，可以拉取远程仓库代码，如果不是代码级深度修改，可不用安装</td></tr></tbody></table><p>明白原理就知道为什么要安装这些软件，接下来逐个介绍怎么安装。</p><h2 id="安装Node-js"><a href="#安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="安装Node.js"></a>安装Node.js</h2><p>下载后直接安装，下载地址：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Node.js</a></p><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h2><ul><li>在Command终端依次执行以下命令</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">cd &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本地Hexo博客文件安装完毕，文件夹结构如下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml //博客配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── db.json</span><br><span class="line">├── debug.log</span><br><span class="line">├── node_modules</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── JSONStream</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── a-sync-waterfall</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">├── package-lock.json</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json</span><br><span class="line">├── public</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── 2018</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── archives</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── ...</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── draft.md</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── page.md</span><br><span class="line">│   └── post.md</span><br><span class="line">├── source</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── _posts //文章存储位置</span><br><span class="line">│   └── images //图片存储位置</span><br><span class="line">└── themes //模板</span><br><span class="line">    ├── landscape</span><br><span class="line">    └── material-x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>启动服务，执行：<br><code>hexo s</code></p></li><li><p>浏览器访问：<br><code>http://localhost:4000/</code><br>若出现Hexo默认博客页面，则本地部署成功。</p></li></ul><h2 id="使用GitHub-Pages"><a href="#使用GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="使用GitHub Pages"></a>使用GitHub Pages</h2><ul><li>注册GitHub账号</li><li>新建仓库，格式：{你GitHub账户名}.github.io</li><li>生成SSH Key，Command执行：<br><code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;邮箱地址&quot;</code></li><li>查看并复制公钥内容：<br><code>cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</code></li><li>GitHub页面右上角=&gt;Settings=&gt;SSH and GPG keys=&gt;New SSH key</li><li>安装插件,command执行：<br><code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></li></ul><h2 id="生成发布"><a href="#生成发布" class="headerlink" title="生成发布"></a>生成发布</h2><p>command执行：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">vi _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文件末尾修改为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:&lt;你Github账号&gt;/&lt;你Github账号&gt;.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意：type, repo和branch的冒号后是有一个空格的，删掉空格发布不会报错，但是文件无法上传至GitHub。</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等待1分钟左右，浏览器访问网址：<br>https://&lt;你Github账号名&gt;.github.io<br>比如我的博客：<br><a href="https://whfghfhw.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://whfghfhw.github.io/</a></p><p>本文参考了以下文章，感谢：</p><blockquote><p><a href="https://www.simon96.online/2018/10/12/hexo-tutorial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.simon96.online/2018/10/12/hexo-tutorial/</a><br><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/jackyroc/p/7681938.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.cnblogs.com/jackyroc/p/7681938.html</a><br><a href="http://cyzus.github.io/2015/06/21/github-build-blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://cyzus.github.io/2015/06/21/github-build-blog/</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
